data.name: grdOrder.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT F.GROUP_SER , A.PKINJ1002 , A.FKINJ1001 , E.FKOCS1003 , C.HANGMOG_NAME , A.SEQ , A.TONGGYE_CODE , A.MAGAM_DATE , A.MAGAM_JANGSO , A.MAGAM_SER , TO_CHAR(A.RESER_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') , A.RESER_TIME , TO_CHAR(A.JUBSU_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') , A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.JUSA_BUUI , A.ACTING_JANGSO , TO_CHAR(A.ACTING_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') , A.ACTING_TIME , A.COMPANY_CODE , A.LOT_NO , A.CHASU_CODE , A.PW_RESULT , A.CS_RESULT , A.AST , NVL(A.ACTING_FLAG,'N') ACTING_FLAG , A.SUNAB_SURYANG , TO_CHAR(A.SUNAB_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') , A.FKOUT1001 FKOUT1001 , DECODE(D.BUNRYU2, '05', '1', DECODE(NVL(F.ANTI_CANCER_YN,'N'), 'X', '1', 'Y', '2', '0')) CANCER_YN , E.BUNHO BUNHO , F.ORDER_REMARK REMARK_CHK , A.DC_YN , A.JUSA_TONG_CNT , A.OTHER_BUSEO_YN , A.JUJONGJA , FN_ADM_LOAD_USER_NAME(A.JUJONGJA) JUJONGJA_NAME , FN_INJ_YEBANG_CHK(A.HANGMOG_CODE) YEBANG_JUJONG_CHK , FN_INJ_LOAD_BANNAB_ACTDAY(E.FKOCS1003, A.RESER_DATE) ACTDAY_CHK , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, A.RESER_DATE) , NVL(F.BANNAB_YN,'N') BANNAB_YN , FN_INJ_SKIN_JUSA_CHK(A.HANGMOG_CODE) SKIN_YN , TO_CHAR(E.CHUNGGU_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') CHUNGGU_DATE , TO_CHAR(E.ORDER_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') ORDER_DATE , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(E.DOCTOR, A.RESER_DATE) DOCTOR , FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI',F.ORD_DANUI) ORD_DANUI , DECODE(F.HOPE_DATE,NULL,'N','Y') HOPE_DATE_YN , F.BOGYONG_CODE || FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA_SPD_GUBUN',NVL(F.JUSA_SPD_GUBUN,'0')) BOGYONG_CODE , F.SURYANG , F.DV , DECODE(F.DV_TIME, '#', '/', F.DV_TIME) , F.SLIP_CODE , F.ORDER_DATE , A.MIX_GROUP , F.HOPE_DATE , F.ORDER_GUBUN FROM OCS1003 F , INJ1001 E , INV0110 D , OCS0103 C , INJ1002 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.HOSP_CODE(+) = C.HOSP_CODE AND E.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND F.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND E.NALSU > 0 AND NVL(E.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND A.FKINJ1001 = E.PKINJ1001 AND A.RESER_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_reser_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND C.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND TO_DATE(:f_reser_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') BETWEEN C.START_DATE AND C.END_DATE AND C.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND D.JAERYO_CODE(+) = C.JAERYO_CODE AND F.PKOCS1003 = E.FKOCS1003 AND NVL(F.WONYOI_ORDER_YN,'N') != 'Y' AND NVL(A.ACTING_FLAG,'N') = 'N' ORDER BY E.GWA, E.DOCTOR, F.GROUP_SER , A.MIX_GROUP, A.HANGMOG_CODE
